# ============================================================
# Scorpius Move — Environment variables (T080)
# ============================================================
# IMPORTANT: use placeholders here, NEVER real keys.
# Real values go in `.env` (gitignored) and are loaded at runtime
# via `process.env.EXPO_PUBLIC_*`.
#
# Why placeholders: keeps git history clean of secrets, prevents
# accidental copy/paste of personal keys, and signals to devs that
# `.env` is where real config lives.
#
# Why it doesn't break security: EXPO_PUBLIC_* values are PUBLIC by
# design (embedded in JS bundle, extractable from compiled app).
# Real security is enforced via Google Cloud Console restrictions
# (bundleId/packagename for Google Maps) and EAS project access
# (for Expo Push). Rotation strategy documented in
# docs/mobile/maps-and-push.md.
# ============================================================

# Copy this file to `.env` and fill in the real values.
# `.env` is gitignored.

# API backend (Hub Laravel)
EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://staging.hub.portalscorpiustecnologia.com.br/api/v1

# Google Maps (T080)
# Get your key em https://console.cloud.google.com/google/maps-apis/credentials
# Restringir por bundleId (iOS) e SHA-1 (Android) no Console.
EXPO_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=AIzaSyXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX

# EAS (Expo Application Services) — Expo Push token T080
# UUID do projeto em https://expo.dev/eas → Project Settings
EXPO_PUBLIC_EAS_PROJECT_ID=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
